<div id="hint-multiselect-markup" class="hint message blue rounded-5 cf">
	<h1>Getting Started: Select Thumbnail(s)</h1>
	<div class='center'><img src='/static/img/hints/multi-select.jpg'></div>
	<p>Use <span class='keypress multiselect-single'>Ctrl-Click</span> to select individual Snaps, or <span class='keypress'>Shift-Click</span> to select a contiguous range.
	Most actions will be applied to all selected Snaps. You can also drag selected Snaps to your <b>Lightbox</b> to hold them in place.</p>
</div>
<div id="hint-contextmenu-markup" class="hint message blue rounded-5 cf">
	<h1>Getting Started: The Context Menu (i.e. Right-Click)</h1>
	<div class='right'><img src='/static/img/hints/contextmenu.jpg'></div>
	<p>Try <span class='keypress'>Right-Click</span> on a Snap, Circle, or Person to see a menu of available actions. 
		Or click on the <img src="/static/img/css-gui/icon2.png" title="Click on this icon to show related actions"> icon.</p>
	<ul>From this menu, you can apply a number of actions to the selected thumbnails
		<li>Rate one or more Snaps</li>
		<li>Group multiple Snaps into a single Shot</li>
		<li>Share Snaps in a Circle</li>
		<li>and much more...</li>
	</ul>
</div>
<div id="hint-create-markup" class="hint message blue rounded-5 cf">
	<h1>Getting Started: Create New Things</h1>
		<p>Click on the <img src="/static/img/hints/create.jpg" title="This is where all the fun begins"> button to create new things.</p>
		<ul>From the Create menu, you can:
		<li>create new Circles and invite friends to join</li>
		<li>import new photos from your desktop</li>
		<li>create or edit Stories to share with friends</li>
	</ul>
</div>
<div id="hint-bestshot-markup" class="hint message blue rounded-5 cf">	
	<h1>Getting Started: Bestshots</h1>
	<div class='right'><img title="This is the Bestshot of 2 similar Snaps" src='/static/img/hints/bestshot.jpg'></div>
	<p>Bestshots are an easy way to keep your Snaps organized and hide duplicate photos. Look for this icon <img title="3 Snaps in this Shot." src='/static/img/css-gui/icon-hidden-shot-3.png'> to identify Bestshots.</p>
	<p>To create a Bestshot, just select similar Snaps and choose "Group as Shot" from the Context Menu. 
	<ul>We'll show just the Bestshot, as determined by:
		<li>a Snap you specifically select, or</li>
		<li>the top-rated Snap in the Shot.</li>
	</ul>
	<p>Remember, hidden Snaps are always just a click away.</p>
</div>
<div id="hint-hiddenshot-markup" class="hint message blue rounded-5 cf">	
	<h1>Show Hidden Snaps</h1>
	<div class='right'><img src='/static/img/hints/hidden-snaps.jpg'></div>
	<ul>Show Hidden Snaps to set your Bestshot. This is done by:
		<li>rating your Snaps, or</li>
		<li>specifically choosing a Bestshot.</li>
	</ul>
	<p>Hidden Snaps are always just a click away. Just look for this <img title="3 Snaps in this Shot." src='/static/img/css-gui/icon-hidden-shot-3.png'> icon to get in on the secret.</p>

</div>
<div id="hint-filmstrip-markup" class="hint message blue rounded-5 cf">	
	<h1>The Filmstrip</h1>
	<div class='center'><img src='/static/img/hints/filmstrip.jpg'></div>
