</div>
<div id="hint-lightbox-markup" class="hint message blue rounded-5 cf">	
	<h1>Getting Started: The Lightbox</h1>
	<div class='center'><img src="/static/img/hints/lightbox.jpg" title"Don't forget about me, I'm way down here at the bottom of the page!"></div>
